Trippy Leaf Token will be used as the governance token for the Trippy Leaf DAO to control Trippy Leaf Business and Brand dealings. It will also be issued as rewards to brand ambassadors,customers registered in the loyalty program etc...
Our reasoning on releasing a Token: Trippy Leaf Token is designed to grow the Trippy Leaf Brand by offering incentives to brand ambassadors, attracting and rewarding customers which they can then be apart of the Trippy Leaf DAO if they choose to. 
This will keep Founders, customers, ambassadors and investors all aligned to make Trippy Leaf as successful as possible. 

